features: 【5 Rotatable Joints 】Crafted to enhance your productivity, this rotatable led desk lamp features 5 rotatable joints, granting you complete control over the direction and height of your lighting. You can rotate the bilateral light bars vertically to change the illumination angle. Turn them up to expand the lighting coverage to illuminates your entire desk or turn them down to create a super bright lighting area for sewing crafting. The office light extends up to an impressive 28 inches in height.

【45°Angled Away Asymmetric Light】Experience gentle, uniform lighting that won't strain your eyes, thanks to our advanced 45° angled away side lighting design and high color rendering index (CRI>90) LEDs, it only illuminates your desk and keyborad rather than your screens and eyes. Our office desk lamp is designed to eliminate distracting glare and flickering while minimizing blue light exposure, effectively reducing eye fatigue and providing accurate color rendering.

【Ambient Lighting & Smart Light Sensor】When the bilateral auxiliary lights shine upwards, they can work as ambient lights to relieve eye strain. The built in light sensor will automatically adjust the brightness accordingly to a comfortable level depending on the surrounding light. The main light and the auxiliary lights of the office lamp need to be turned on or off separately, but the brightness and color temperatures are controlled together.

【Stability And Convenience】Unlike clip-on led table lamps that require specific table types, the Micomlan desk l for home office boasts a stable 8-inch diameter heavy round base with anti-slip pads, making it suitable for any table, workbench, or desk. Adjust your lighting parameters and illumination directions with confidence, knowing your lamp stands securely.

【Versatile Lighting Modes】Customize your lighting experience with ease using the adjustable desk lamp's five color temperature modes, each offering five brightness levels. A sensitive touch sensor allows you to effortlessly toggle between these modes and brightness levels. For precise dimming and tempering, simply long-press the panel. Plus, the memory function retains your previous lighting settings, ensuring your preferred ambiance every time you switch it on.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Featuring 5 strongly damped rotatable joints, 3 ultra-bright light bars and 28.2 inches working height, this desk lamp allows for freely vertical and horizontal adjustments to create a fully customizable lighting experience. You can raise the desk lamp and turn the bilateral lights up to expand the lighting coverage, or you can lower the lamp and turn the bilateral lights down to focus on specific activities like sewing and crafting.

Illuminate your entire workspace with the Micomlan rotatable desk light bar. The desk lamp is capable of covering a large desk and evenly distributing the light. The support adjustable swing arms have enough flexibility to twist and turn into almost any situation, which allows you to easily direct the light where you need it most.

When the bilateral light bars shine upwards, they can work as ambients lights to relieve your eye strain.The built in smart light sensor will automatically adjust the brightness accordingly to a comfortable level depending on the surrounding light.The versatile led desk lamp provides 5 levels of brightness and color temperature to choose from with the touch of a button.

Unlike clip-on led table lamps that require specific table types, the Micomlan desk light for home office boasts a stable 8-inch diameter heavy round base with anti-slip pads, making it suitable for any table, workbench, or desk.

You won't get tired with prolonged use.It can be used for studying, reading, handcrafting, design, sewing, working to meet the needs for clear lighting.Easy to install and use. reviews.reviewText: I have had a lot of different lamps in my home office over the last 20 years. Nothing compares to this lamp. It is tall, versatile, and easy to turn on and off. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for a standard jewelers bench
reviews.reviewText: This is the perfect lamp for a jewelers bench that has edges that won't fit a c-clamp style work lamp. The base is flat so that you can sit tools on it (meaning it's not in the way because it's a usable surface) and it looks sleek. The brightness and color temperature levels are a great touch. Because the hinge style doesn't require that the main arm bend backward in order to lower down the lights, it can fit against a wall in a corner. I hope it lasts because the design is just what I've been looking for on my bench.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Terrific brightness and good adustability
reviews.reviewText: This desk lamp really makes my work surface bright and productive. Being able to adjust the light temperature is nice and the brightness controls are very good. My only negative to note is that the base should either be heavier or more elongated to support the lamp head if extended forward. That is, the lamp is wobbly if not mostly extended up versus extended out.
